ShinyCMS Features
=================

A list of features that are present and working* in the current version of the 
code.

* more or less.


* CMS Pages
	* Render page using on-disk template and in-database content

* User area
	* Log in / out
	* Edit details
	* Roles ('page admin', 'template admin', etc)

* Blogs
	* Display post
	* Display (nested/threaded) comments

